Data transfers. System design.

Functions:
void vProcessData(void) // vProcessData() is a medium priority task


* On incomming data:
if issuspended(vProcessData) then
	resume(vProcessData)
end if


* On processing complete:
suspend(vProcessData)


* On resume (OS stuff):
if no_higher_priority_tasks then
	vProcessData()
else
	run_other_task()
end if
	

